Date: 2026-03-03
Checkpoint: data/checkpoints/best.pt (epoch 299, loss 0.000009)
Max steps: 250, chunk_exec=5, ensemble_k=0.01

Inference techniques:
  1. Temporal ensembling (ACT paper): re-plan every 5 steps,
     exponentially-weighted average of overlapping action chunks
  2. Hierarchical task decomposition: composite tasks (pick, place)
     first use "grasp" embedding to approach, switch to task-specific
     embedding after auto-grasp triggers
  3. Auto-release for place: hand_z < target_z + 0.12 && cube_xy < 6cm
  4. Gravity simulation: after release in kinematic mode, drop cube to table

